4. Tracy Brown

# Tracy Brown

## Manager Web And Mobile Applications

Email: **[tbrown@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:tbrown@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Tracy joined TACC in April 2017 and is involved in several software projects that develop web portal applications. Tracy is the project lead for the DesignSafe user portal and helps manage the user information and interfaces for other portals such as Frontera, UTRC, 3DEM.org, and many more. Tracy has worked to UT Austin for 29 years. Prior to joining TACC, Tracy worked on the main UT Austin campus. She began as a Software Developer in ITS and then worked for 15 years as a Senior IT Manger for administrative application development teams in the Development Office and the College of Liberal Arts. From 2014-2017 she served as Director of Institutional Reporting and Research in the Provosts' Office.

### Education

**B.S. Computer Science,**  

Texas State University, 1992